{"tid":2516883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登與前總統卡特夫婦合照變巨人引熱議","createTime":"2021-05-05T03:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:18:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd42d55dffd9fdfb0aa7612fed2161146569f196","tid":2516883,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕網路上因鏡頭、錯位、攝影方式不同意外產生的趣味照片不勝枚舉，但發生在美國總統身上就相當罕見了。美總統拜登夫婦近日拜訪前總統卡特夫婦，4人合照卻因攝影師使用廣角鏡頭，身體比例看起來差異相當大，引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n《BBC》報導，由卡特夫婦創辦的非營利組織「卡特中心」PO出一張拜登夫婦到訪的照片，卡特與妻子羅莎琳靠內坐在沙發上，拜登與妻子吉兒則分別蹲在右、左側。但從畫面上來看，即便超過180公分的拜登比卡特略高，夫婦2人的身形明顯是巨人尺寸。<br />\n<br />\nBBC攝影編輯庫姆斯（Phil Coomes）解釋，因為這張照片使用了廣角鏡頭，導致鏡頭兩側的畫面被放大。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3521314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3521314&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a7499018\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3521314&h=730cdb7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3521314</a>"},{"pid":"60fad2943b998c1951f21781e37f50bee16f80ad","tid":2516883,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:11:51.000Z","msg":"堂堂總統靠呢d小技巧自high <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ca615bac140ec3cf5ec60b5245f52ddb5cd5fc","tid":2516883,"uid":277031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"princejoyce.jpg"},{"pid":"cfd1070106e984264c859dc49ae9bfbb120b244f","tid":2516883,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"登登真係好愛幼幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5966c632cb4925628ecc1af045714af494f502","tid":2516883,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:16:51.000Z","ms